fullplot: Mick and Sue continue where they left off in "'Crocodile' Dundee". New York drug lords are pursuing Sue for having solid evidence against them for murder, so for her safety, Mick takes her back to Australia. When the gangsters follow them, Mick demonstrates his outback skills once more.
plot: Australian outback expert protects his New York love from gangsters who've followed her down under.
title: Crocodile Dundee II
